text:
First aur second year mein kaafi mazze kie the apan ne, kaafi fifa mein tunne haraya, el classico mein Madrid k jeetne k baad kaafi pareshan kia mujhe xD aur kaafi memories h bhai. 
Apni last party due h aur kabhi bhi same city mein hua to milunga tujse, kaafi baatein krni h tujhse.
author: Rishab  Agarwal

text: Maine life mein tujhse zyada modest banda nhi dekha. Talented to tu h hi but most importantly apne aas pass k logon ko khush rakhta h. Aage bhi aisse hi chaapte aur phukte rehna.
author: Rishab  Agarwal

text:
Thanks for being such a good friend and helping me selflessly during my entire stay at IIT Kanpur in every aspect possible. I know I have not always been in my best behaviour but I want you to know that you can ask me anything in future if you want. I will just be a call away. 

You are a great person and deserve all the happiness in the world.
author: Rishab  Agarwal

text: I like our discussion related to barca and football in general. Maaza aaya tere saath iss Auli trip mein.

text:
Dhanbad to Delhi to Kanpur, kitti memories h. Kaafi zyada mehnati banda h tu aur moody bhi. Kaafi zyada close h tu merese aur hamesha rahega no matter what. I am always a call away bhai.

Plus, ik agar ye sab tmko in person bol rhe hote to tu bolta 'saala senti pgla gya h' xD. Lambi trip plan krte h bhai iss covid k baad saath mein. 
Thanks for being a part of my life.
